data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 2-car garage, pool home with an inviting open floor plan. Recent upgrades include a new AC Unit and Water Heater in 2022. Kitchen features granite countertops and ample cabinet storage along with SS Appliances. The home has a 12x10 shed with electric and a water filtration system. Enjoy tranquility in the spacious, fenced backyard that offers a serene setting. It has a screened and covered Lanai for you to enjoy your morning cup of coffee or tea, and enjoy your favorite beverage in the evening. Come enjoy the Florida Lifestyle in this amazing home. The home is nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, conveniently located near beaches, parks, shopping, dining, schools, I-95, FL Turnpike. Great opportunity to own this delightful home.
